<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Volunteer Invoice</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #0e2f52; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #f8f9fa; }
        .email-container { background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(9, 135, 201, 0.1); }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0987c9, #7ed956); color: white; padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center; }
        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; }
        .header p { margin: 10px 0 0 0; opacity: 0.9; font-size: 16px; }
        .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
        .content > p { color: #5a6c7d; margin: 0 0 20px 0; }
        .content p strong { color: #0e2f52; }
        .invoice-card { background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 12px; padding: 25px; margin: 25px 0; }
        .invoice-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding-bottom: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 2px solid #0987c9; }
        .invoice-from { }
        .invoice-from .label { font-size: 12px; color: #5a6c7d; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .invoice-from .name { font-size: 16px; color: #0e2f52; font-weight: 600; }
        .invoice-from .email { font-size: 14px; color: #5a6c7d; }
        .invoice-number { text-align: right; }
        .invoice-number .label { font-size: 12px; color: #5a6c7d; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .invoice-number .value { font-size: 16px; color: #0987c9; font-weight: 700; }
        .detail-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
        .detail-row:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; }
        .detail-label { color: #5a6c7d; font-size: 14px; }
        .detail-value { color: #0e2f52; font-weight: 500; }
        .total-row { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0987c9, #7ed956); border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin-top: 15px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
        .total-row .label { color: white; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; }
        .total-row .value { color: white; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; }
        .payment-info { background: #fef3c7; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin-top: 25px; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; }
        .payment-info h3 { margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #92400e; font-size: 16px; }
        .payment-info p { margin: 0; color: #92400e; font-size: 14px; }
        .attachment-note { background: #e0f2fe; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin-top: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .attachment-note p { margin: 0; color: #0369a1; font-size: 14px; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 25px 30px; background: #f8f9fa; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
        .footer p { margin: 0; color: #5a6c7d; font-size: 14px; }
        .footer .brand { color: #0987c9; font-weight: 600; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Volunteer Invoice</h1>
            <p>Invoice #<%= invoiceNumber %></p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <strong><%= organizationName %></strong>,</p>
            <p>A volunteer has completed their service for your event. Please find the invoice details below:</p>

            <div class="invoice-card">
                <div class="invoice-header">
                    <div class="invoice-from">
                        <div class="label">From</div>
                        <div class="name"><%= studentName %></div>
                        <div class="email"><%= studentEmail %></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="invoice-number">
                        <div class="label">Invoice #</div>
                        <div class="value"><%= invoiceNumber %></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Event</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= eventTitle %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Event Date</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= eventDate %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Hours Worked</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= hours %> hours</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Hourly Rate</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= currency %> <%= hourlyRate %></span>
                </div>

                <div class="total-row">
                    <span class="label">Total Amount Due</span>
                    <span class="value"><%= currency %> <%= amount %></span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="attachment-note">
                <p>The full invoice PDF is attached to this email.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="payment-info">
                <h3>Payment Instructions</h3>
                <p>Please process this payment via bank transfer directly to the volunteer using the bank details provided in the attached PDF. Once the volunteer confirms receipt of payment, this invoice will be marked as paid in our system.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p><span class="brand">Volunteens</span> - Connecting young volunteers with opportunities</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
